{"word":"G2400 - ἰδού - idoú - id-oo' - Behold","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἰδού</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">idoú</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">id-oo'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Behold</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>NA / Not Available</span>"},{"paragraph":"அதோ, அங்கே, அப்பொழுது - எச்சம்"},{"paragraph":"Behold! See! Lo!"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Second person singular imperative middle voice of <a href=\"#/G1492 - εἴδω - eídō - i'-do/1492\">G1492</a>; used as imperative <i>lo!</i>: - behold, lo, see.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}